<body style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: #f6f6f6; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
				
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" src="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.file.force.com/file-asset-public/Alliance_Rural_Remote_Email_heade?oid=00DAD00000BK4sL" style="max-width: 683.05px" title="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;">
						<p>Dear&nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

						<p>Thank you once again for recently completing a reference check for<br />
						<strong>XXXXXXXXXX&nbsp;</strong>– we really appreciate your time.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						When completing the reference, you indicated interest in hearing more about job opportunities through our company, so I’m pleased to share some information with you today.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Attached, you’ll find:</p>

						<ul>
							<li><strong>Our Client Proposal</strong>&nbsp;– outlining who we are, our 20+ years of experience supporting Rural &amp; Remote communities across Australia, and the rigorous process we take our nurses through to ensure they are fully “work ready” when&nbsp;they arrive at your facility.</li>
							<li><strong>Our Current Rates&nbsp;</strong>– covering Labour Hire (agency payroll). We also offer a Fee for Service option (client payroll) and would be happy to provide more details if that may be of interest.</li>
						</ul>

						<p>&nbsp;<br />
						<strong>Terms of Business</strong><br />
						In order to&nbsp;provide nursing staff, we’ll need a Terms of Business (TOB) in place. To prepare this document, could you kindly provide the following details:</p>

						<ul>
							<li>Legal business name of your organisation</li>
							<li>ABN</li>
							<li>Address (please confirm if this should be your corporate head office or set up under each facility)</li>
							<li>Phone number</li>
							<li>Billing contact name, email, and address (if different)</li>
							<li>Authorised signatory’s name and email</li>
							<li>Your preference for <strong>Labour Hire (Agency Payroll)</strong>&nbsp;and/or&nbsp;<strong>Fee for Service (Client Payroll)</strong>&nbsp;– as we prepare separate TOBs for each option</li>
						</ul>

						<p>Once we have this information, we’ll generate the TOB for electronic signature via our secure portal,&nbsp;ContractPodAi&nbsp;(emails will come from Business Australia or Business NSW). If you’d prefer to review the draft before signing, we can send it through directly.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						<strong>A Note on Labour Hire Rates</strong><br />
						Our agency payroll (Labour Hire) charge rates also incorporate:</p>

						<ul>
							<li>Mandatory training (completed before any placement)&nbsp;</li>
							<li>Statutory obligations and employment liabilities including superannuation, payroll tax, insurances, wages, and workers’ compensation</li>
							<li>National criminal history checks</li>
							<li>Reduced administrative/HR burden for your facility, as onboarding is streamlined</li>
						</ul>

						<p>We’d be delighted to partner with you and support your staffing needs. Please don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions – I’d be more than happy to discuss further.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Kind regards,<br />
						{{{Sender.FirstName}}}&nbsp;{{{Sender.LastName}}}<br />
						Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
